568
00:42:11.590 --> 00:42:16.350
Hej, je to chvíle!

569
00:42:16.350 --> 00:42:17.750
Jaký osud nás zde svedl dohromady?

570
00:42:17.750 --> 00:42:20.450
Už je to chvíle!

571
00:42:24.320 --> 00:42:28.390
